Nutrient data for: CADBURY CHOCOLATE, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622210459176
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

Ingredients: MILK**, sugar, vegetable fats (palm, shea), cocoa butter, cocoa mass, dried whey (from MILK), dried CREAM, dried skimmed MILK, MILK fat, WHEAT flour, emulsifiers (E442, SOYA lecithin, E476, sunflower lecithin), flavourings, fat-reduced cocoa powder, WHEAT starch, glucose-fructose syrup, salt, acidity regulators (E501, sodium bicarbonate), raising agent (ammonium bicarbonate). **The equivalent of 426ml of fresh liquid milk in every 227g of milk chocolateMILK CHOCOLATE: MILK SOLIDS 20% MINIMUM, ACTUAL 23%.CONTAINS VEGETABLE FATS IN ADDITION TO COCOA BUTTER. MAY CONTAIN NUTS AND EGG. Date available: 11/10/2017 Date last updated by company: 05/17/2017
